<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038142" n="1"/> <pb facs="1038143" n="2"/> <pb facs="1038144" n="3"/> <pb facs="1038145" n="4"/>
  <opener><salute>Viro <abbr>pl.</abbr> Reverendo et Celeberrimo
    <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobo Hermanno</rs> <abbr>S. P. D. N. B.</abbr></salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Diutius <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quo Tibi et merito quidem videbor distulisse debitam Tibi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me gra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiarum actionem tum pro voto quo cathedram Mathematicam mihi delatam
    <lb/>et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me tribus abhinc mensibus occupatam gratulari voluisti, tum pro iis,
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> me hac ex occasione monere dignatus es. Sed debiti hujus, quo me
    <lb/>citius liberare maluissem, persolutionem hactenus impedivere
    <lb/>negotia et cur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quibus post meum in hanc <rs type="place">urbem</rs> adventum fere oppress<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>us fui. Accessit ingens ex funesta
    <lb/>et inopinata morte <rs type="persons">Parentis</rs> mei, sub initium fere inaugurationis
    <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> defuncti conceptus dolor, qui molestias novi vit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>generis non leviter auxit, et è contrario requiem animi mihi su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>opere
    <lb/>necessariam vehementer imminuit. Nunc autem paululum mihi redditus
    <lb/>has ad Te depropero, ut de grato meo in Te animo Tibi constet, Teque
    <lb/>simul rogitem, ut pro amicitia quam mihi indulges, me porro mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nere pergas circa ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me in eodem quo tu olim loco nunc constituto optime fieri
    <lb/>posse judicas. Gratum facies, si genium <rs type="persons">Professorum</rs> nostrorum mihi
    <lb/>describes, et qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipsorum intuitu cavenda esse expertus es significabis. Ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine fere familiariter utor nisi <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchione <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Poleni</rs>, <abbr>DDos.</abbr> <abbr>P.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055630597">Burgos</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055630597">Vallisneri</rs>,
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-104265264">Morgagni</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-12898497X">Lazarini</rs> nonnunquam sed raro adeo; reliqui mihi
    <lb/>fere sunt barbari aut ego illis. <rs type="person">Petrus</rs> famulus olim Tuus
    <pb facs="1038143" n="2"/>
    <lb/>et mihi nunc servit. Nequam iste <rs type="person">uxore</rs>, quam in Patria duxerat, deserta
    <lb/>sub idem fere tempus quo ego in hanc <rs type="place">urbem</rs> venerat. Suspicor eum brevi
    <lb/>ad <rs type="person">uxorem</rs> rediturum esse, interim tamen gratum mihi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stabis, si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de
    <lb/>fide ejus tibi constant, et quonam stipendio illum mactare solitus fueris, mihi
    <lb/>nuntiare non dedignaberis. Vidi hic impudentissimi <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzagli<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="biblio">libellum</rs>
    <lb/>famosum, et stupui hominis audaciam et nequitiam. Recte facies si be<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stiam hanc posthac suo more vivere sines, cum qua disputare et ego
    <lb/>indecens esse puto optarem tamen ut <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quodam sub ficto aut tecto no<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine perstringeretur, quod fortassis ab amico quodam tuo fieri poterit.
    <lb/>Risum mihi <abbr>mo.</abbr> vit dum in solutione sua Problematis mei distinguit
    <lb/>inter distantiam finitam et infinitam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> centro. Verum est <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156361761">Checozzi</rs>
    <lb/>solam dedisse syntheticam demonstrationem solutionis <!-- Eine Zeile war gar nicht an der Stelle transkribiert worden, sondern stand ganz am Schluss. Transkription überprüft und oben hier eingefügt. MK 11.12.2024  -->
    <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>, sed quum illa talis sit, ut synthesis ipsius in analysin conversa solis
    <lb/>Parabolis aut hyperbolis applicari possit, tamdiu suspicabor eum
    <lb/>in analysi sua supposuisse, Curvam fore aliquam ex genere para<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bolarum, donec aliquam analysin ab omni tali suppositione liberam
    <lb/>proferat. Plane non assequor, quod dicis, Problema hac, data scala vel
    <lb/>virium vel temporum invenire alteram generaliter loquendo solvi non
    <lb/>posse seu implicare. An ergo si curva virium sit <abbr>ex.</abbr> <abbr>gr.</abbr> hyperbola ad
    <lb/>axem relata, mobile his viribus sollicitatum recta descendere non
    <lb/>poterit? Si sensum tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> assertionis capio videris affirmare, mobile
    <lb/>recta descendere non posse, nisi urgeatur in singulis punctis vi qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>sit ut dignitas aliqua distanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> centro; hoc autem verum esse mihi vix
    <lb/>persuadebis. Igitur cum mobile aliis viribus sollicitatum etiam descendere
    <lb/>possit et quidem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quiete ex diversis distantiis, tempora descensuum expri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mi poterunt per rectas lineas constituentes ordinatas curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cujusdam
    <lb/>et cuilibet dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scal<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> virium respondebit aliqua scala temporum et
    <lb/>vicissim, adeo ut non videam, quomodo dicere possis Problema esse im<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>
    <pb facs="1038144" n="3"/> 
    <lb/>possibile et implicare quoties scala data non sit una ex genere parabolarum.
    <lb/>Ego vero mihi videor Problema posse solvere generaliter illud Problema, et ex
    <lb/>illa solutione <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> priori deducere <rs type="keyword">parabolam Cubicam</rs> satisfacientem Proble<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mati <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me <rs type="persons">Italis</rs> proposito. </p>
  <closer>Vale et me ama. <lb/><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs>. <date when="1717-03-24">24 Mart 1717</date>.</dateline></closer>
  <pb facs="1038145" n="4"/> 
